<item>
            <title>[LU-5815] d_count redefined in lustre 2.6.0 and in sles11sp3 3.0.101-0.35.1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5815</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&quot;d_count&quot; is defined at&lt;br/&gt;
lustre 2.6.0&lt;br/&gt;
    lustre/include/linux/lustre_patchless_compat.h,  line 123&lt;br/&gt;
and&lt;br/&gt;
sles11sp3 3.0.101-0.35.0&lt;br/&gt;
    include/linux/dcache.h, line 153.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &apos;#define d_count&apos; is new in sles11sp3 3.0.101-0.35.1, (Not in -0.31.1)&lt;br/&gt;
and &apos;#define d_count&apos; was named &apos;#define  d_refcount&apos; in 2.4.3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now we have redefined symbols.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="27333">LU-5815</key>
